text: @ewarren Raises hand. #Unemployed in Massachusetts. I'll be broke when the Emergency COVID-19 Relief FMLA runs out. Even 1,200 more dollars won't pay my bills. As for potential trolls, no I'm not uneducated or lazy, just a medically frahile woman who wants to see her kids grow up.
